705780f-a.title: Brooklyn: Montieth Street - Stanwix Street
705780f-a.text:
Monteith Street, north side, west from Stanwix
Street. Also shown are W. P. A. men working on a
sewer project.
July 11, 1935
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Profect
